# Project artefacts
data/papers/
data/golden/raw/
# Harvested golden-candidate stubs are pre-review WIP (CONTRIBUTING:
# work-in-progress never gets committed). Promoted, human-labelled ones
# land in the tracked data/golden/<set>.yaml via scripts.promote_candidates.
data/golden/_candidates/
data/eval/runs/
data/figures/
# data/pages/ holds rendered page PNGs. The 20-paper curated demo corpus
# (arXiv ids 2604.*) is committed so CI can build the deploy image without
# a slow CPU bge-m3 bake step. Other paper-id dirs (local user "BYO PDFs"
# renders, MMLongBench scratch) stay gitignored.
data/pages/*
!data/pages/.gitkeep
!data/pages/2604.*
# qdrant_local/ — baked Qdrant snapshot for the deploy image. Committed
# alongside data/pages/2604.* so CI does only `docker build` + `docker push`.
# Local users running bootstrap_corpus against their own PDFs would write
# here too — those changes show as git diffs and can be ignored or
# committed to a fork branch.
# (Previously gitignored entirely; baked-in path mode now.)
# Portalocker sentinel — transient on every open, no value in tracking.
qdrant_local/.lock
# Curated demo manifest only — the PDFs themselves are fetched from arXiv
# on demand and never committed.
data/curated_demo/*
!data/curated_demo/papers.txt
# MMLongBench-Doc parquet (~5 MB) + PDFs (~650 MB) — fetched by
# scripts/fetch_mmlongbench.py; the derived golden YAML at
# data/golden/mmlongbench-v1.yaml is the only committed artefact.
# (Trailing comments aren't valid in .gitignore — keep them on their own line
# or git treats the whole "pattern   # comment" string as a literal pattern.)
data/mmlongbench/
logs/
*.log
.langfuse/
qdrant_storage/
postgres_data/

# Coding-agent / LLM-tooling local state and agent-specific docs
.claude/
.cursor/
.windsurfrules
.aider*
CLAUDE.md
GEMINI.md
AGENTS.md
docs/superpowers/

# Git worktrees (isolated dev workspaces)
.worktrees/

# Coverage / packaging leftovers
.coverage.*
coverage.xml
.tox/
__pypackages__/

# Internal rolling-state notes (per-author project tracking; not for public repo)
STATUS.md
docs/mvp-plan.md

# Terraform local state (.terraform.lock.hcl IS committed for provider pinning)
**/.terraform/
*.tfstate
*.tfstate.*
*.tfplan

# Secrets
*.pem
*.key
secrets/
data/eval/ingestion/overlays/**/*.png

# Manual ingestion-study artefacts (ADR 0022 follow-up). Folder of
# per-paper JSONL inventories, page overlays, and per-label contact
# sheets, regenerated by scripts/dump_ingestion_study.py. Local-only.
data/ingestion_study/
# Ad-hoc inspection folders the experiment scripts drop crops into.
# Same pattern as ingestion_study — regenerable from Qdrant.
data/tiny_figures_inspect/
data/unlabeled_inspect/
# Single-paper smoke-test corpora used to probe ingestion changes.
data/papers_one/
data/papers_*_smoke/
